新聞報導，卡達正在研發遙控太陽能遮蔽體，能用來冷卻國內足球場，讓這個富有的波斯灣小國再度成為話題焦點。

大約一星期前，《[The Peninsula](http://thepeninsulaqatar.com/qatar/146510-qu-designs-
cloud-to-cool-your-corner-of-the-earth.html
"http://thepeninsulaqatar.com/qatar/146510-qu-designs-cloud-to-cool-your-
corner-of-the-
earth.html")》報紙引述一份阿拉伯文報刊的消息，刊登一篇共三段的簡短報導，描述卡達大學正在研發「人工雲」，可幫助體育場降溫。

[![Qatar University's "artificial cloud" stadium. Image from Qatar
University.](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2011/03/7358828-375x230.jpg)](https://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hant/?attachment_id=212495)

卡達大學的「人工雲」球場，圖片來自卡達大學

兩天後，英國廣播公司BBC[體育版](http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/9435035.stm
"http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/9435035.stm")亦提及此事，更加上卡達大學所提供的「機器雲」模擬片段。

再隔一天，美國有線電視新聞網CNN也跟進：

截至目前為止，報導的媒體已包括《[時代](http://newsfeed.time.com/2011/03/27/robotic-clouds-will-
provide-shade-during-qatar-world-cup/
"http://newsfeed.time.com/2011/03/27/robotic-clouds-will-provide-shade-during-
qatar-world-cup/")》雜誌、美國[NBC
Sports](http://offthebench.nbcsports.com/2011/03/24/remote-control-artificial-
cloud-to-cool-spectators-at-2022-world-cup/
"http://offthebench.nbcsports.com/2011/03/24/remote-control-artificial-cloud-
to-cool-spectators-at-2022-world-cup/")、《[Fast
Company](http://www.fastcompany.com/1742615/remote-control-clouds-incoming-
for-qatari-2012-world-cup "http://www.fastcompany.com/1742615/remote-control-
clouds-incoming-for-qatari-2012-world-cup")》、[Bldg
Blog](http://bldgblog.blogspot.com/2011/03/cloud-tent.html
"http://bldgblog.blogspot.com/2011/03/cloud-
